      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ROCKABILLY (4) resumed off two close-up placings but didn't finish it off at Ipswich when well in the market. Has the blinkers on for the first time and maps well. Metro-trained and sharp improvement is likely at this level. MAJESTIC LOUVRE (2) resumes and two back wasn't beaten far at Doomben. Has trialled well here and at the Gold Coast and the local can come back further improved and give a good sight. INSAIN LADY (8) has threatened on a number of occasions this preparation and forget the latest when she was outgraded at Eagle Farm. She may control the race from the inside barrier and will be suited back to the shorter sprint. TREFOIL (9) is third-up and will find this easier than Doomben the latest. In a strong city stable and expect to see more from him.",
